171 A.3d 1260 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. JOHANNA CASSIMORE, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-225 Sept.Term 2017

079436 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-919/2793-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
